{"id":6311,"date":"2014-12-23T08:47:55","date_gmt":"2014-12-23T07:47:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=6311"},"modified":"2014-12-23T08:47:55","modified_gmt":"2014-12-23T07:47:55","slug":"tpi-awards-2015-we-made-the-shortlist-for-the-favourite-tour-industry-catering-company","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tpi-awards-2015-we-made-the-shortlist-for-the-favourite-tour-industry-catering-company\/","title":{"rendered":"TPi Awards 2015 &#8211; We made the shortlist for the Favourite Tour Industry Catering Company"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2013 saw us pick up one of the most prestigious catering contracts in the industry, the European tour for <a title=\"Catering Cirque du Soleil\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2014\/12\/being-awarded-the-cirque-du-soleil-european-tour-catering-contract\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cirque du Soleil<\/strong> <\/a>which got our production team and chefs packing our road-cases and off touring arenas all over Europe with both Dralion and Quidam. And just when we thought it couldn\u2019t get any better, in early 2014 Red Radish picked up the backstage crew and artist <a title=\"Wilderness, Lovebox. Somersault, Global Gathering Catering\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2014\/12\/red-radish-win-the-prestigious-mama-co-crew-and-artist-catering-contract\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>catering contracts for the super cool Mama and Co<\/strong><\/a> festivals, Lovebox, Global Gathering, Somersault and the award winning Wilderness in Oxfordshire. So imagine how chuffed we all were when we found out that we had been <span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b>nominated<\/b><\/span>\u00a0for a TPi award for Favourite International Tour Caterer. All the big names were on the list of nominees including Eat to the Beat, Global Infusion Group, Eat Your Hearts Out and even the Cirque du Soleil <strong>North American caterer Spectrum<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It was a great surprise and the perfect end to a wonderful year of work with exciting new clients and our old favourites <a title=\"Glastonbury  Catering\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2014\/12\/festival-crew-and-artist-catering-for-shangri-la-at-glastonbury\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Shangri-La<\/strong><\/a> and The Common at Glastonbury, plus of course Hampton Court Palace, Electric Picnic and Carfest to name but a few. Things could not seemingly get any better and then\u2026 we found out that we had been voted on to the renowned\u00a0<strong><a title=\"Tpi Awards Shortlist\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tpiawards.com\/shortlist\/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">TPi awards <\/a>SHORTLIST\u00a0<\/strong>alongside\u00a0established industry FAVOURITES like Aggreko, Popcorn Catering, \u00a0Gallowglass and Rock-It Cargo, plus world famous artists including Ed Sheeran and One Direction. <strong>How lucky are we!!!<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32.png\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[6311]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6319\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-12-23 at 07.23.32\" width=\"705\" height=\"806\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32.png 705w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32-600x686.png 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32-262x300.png 262w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.23.32-270x309.png 270w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 705px) 100vw, 705px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36.png\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[6311]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6321\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36.png\" alt=\"Tpi Awards Shortlist including best live production\" width=\"700\" height=\"1070\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36.png 700w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36-600x917.png 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36-196x300.png 196w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36-669x1024.png 669w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-23-at-07.24.36-202x309.png 202w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>2013 saw us pick up one of the most prestigious catering contracts in the industry, the European tour for Cirque du Soleil which got our production team and chefs packing&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tpi-awards-2015-we-made-the-shortlist-for-the-favourite-tour-industry-catering-company\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6313,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6311","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-latest-blog-postings"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/word